@NODE Grenzen

This demo has some limitations which are listed below:

À Scenes or rendered pictures can not be stored.

À The maximum resolution for rendering pictures is
  320*256 pixels.

À The additional modules "raytracer" and "scanline" are
  not included. Therefore mirrorings are only partly
  possible and shadows can't be rendered. "Scanline" is
  available from within the editor.

À Utilities like Animbuilder and additional modules are
  missing.

À Some scenes, lots of textures und two fonts are not included.

À The optimized program versions for FPU and 68020-CPU are
  not included.
@ENDNODE

